   <p><b>Do you sell digital downloads so I can make a print myself?</b></p>\r\n\r\n      <p>\r\n        Yes, all prints on the website have a digital download option. This\r\n        allows you to print the photograph yourself. The file is a high\r\n        resolution jpeg and allows you to print any of the sizes available on\r\n        the website.\r\n      </p>\r\n      <br>\r\n\r\n      <p><b>Is each print limited to a certain number?</b></p>\r\n\r\n      <p>\r\n        Yes, all my prints have a limited run of twenty copies. Once they're\r\n        sold out they are no longer printed. Each print has a Certificate Of\r\n        Authenticity which is signed and edition numbered.\r\n      </p>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p><b>What is the quality of your prints?</b></p>\r\n\r\n      <p>\r\n        All my prints use the same high quality, museum grade, Fine Art 310GSM,\r\n        archival cotton rag paper. It's a matte finish and has a beautiful\r\n        texture. Being 310GSM it is a thick paper print and you'll feel the\r\n        quality straight away.\r\n      </p>\r\n      <br>\r\n\r\n      <p><b>What is the exact size of you prints?</b></p>\r\n\r\n      <p>\r\n        These are the exact sizes in mm. 400mm x 600mm 600mm x 900mm 800mm x\r\n        1200mm\r\n      </p>\r\n\r\n      <br>\r\n\r\n      <p><b>Do your prints have white borders?</b></p>\r\n\r\n      <p>\r\n        Yes, my prints have a white boarder around the print. The boarder size\r\n        is dependent on the size of the print and whether the print is framed or\r\n        not. Print only usually have a 15mm white boarder.\r\n      </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <section id=\"contact\">\r\n      <p>Join The Newsletter</p>\r\n      <form action=\"\">\r\n        <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email Address\" aria-label=\"Email Address\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn2\">SIGN UP</button>\r\n      </form>\r\n      <div class=\"social\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/saltlens.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\r\n        <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/saltlens.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\r\n        <a href=\"mailto:youremail@example.com\"><i class=\"fa-regular fa-envelope\"></i></a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n    <footer>\r\n      <p>\r\n        2023 &copy;\r\n        <a href=\"mailto:rafaelfelic@gmail.com\">Rafael Feliciano</a>. Inovating\r\n        solutions\r\n      </p>\r\n    </footer>\r\n    <script src=\"/549b6b2bff82a0ad6730c0f1cd665a19.js\"></script>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n"},"sourceMaps":null,"error":null,"hash":"415ddc815df8b01736eb643948d555dd","cacheData":{}}